Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Intention
---
I desire not to desire, for my will is without value, since I am
ignorant in any case.  Therefore choose Thou for me what Thou knowest
to be best and do not put my perdition in what my autonomy and free
choice prefer.
